          <characteristics>
            <characteristic name="Keywords" typeId="b977-7c5e-33b2-428e">^^**Exalted**^^</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="fd7f-888d-3257-a12b">Each time a model in a friendly non-**^^Hero Daughters of Khaine^^** unit is slain by a combat attack, if that friendly unit is within this unit&apos;s combat range and that model was in combat with the attacking unit, roll a dice. If that friendly unit is a **Blood Sisters** or a **Blood Stalkers** unit, roll 2 dice instead. For each 5+, inflict 1 mortal damage on the attacking unit after the **^^Fight^^** ability has been resolved.</characteristic>
