            <characteristic name="Timing" typeId="652c-3d84-4e7-14f4">Any Charge Phase</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick a visible friendly **^^Daughters of Khaine^^** unit that is wholly within 12&quot; of this unit and is in combat with an enemy unit that charged this turn to be the target. If there are any friendly **Slaughter Queens on Cauldrons of Blood** on the battlefield, you can pick another eligible unit to be a second target.</characteristic>
