            <characteristic name="Declare" typeId="bad3-f9c5-ba46-18cb">Pick a friendly **^^Daughters of Khaine^^** **^^Manifestation^^** wholly within 12&quot; of this unit to be the target.</characteristic>
            <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="b6f1-ba36-6cd-3b03">Roll a dice. On a 3+, the target cannot be picked to be the target of **^^Banish^^** abilities used by enemy units until the start of your next turn.</characteristic>
