                        <characteristic name="Effect" typeId="fd7f-888d-3257-a12b">Shooting attacks that target this unit cannot score critical hits (treat them as regular hits instead). If the unmodified hit roll for a shooting attack that targets this unit is 6, the attack fails and the attack sequence ends.</characteristic>
